response.overview: Multibird is a Bird-Bird Show concert by Bird - Thongchai McIntyre and his first concert after being honored as a National Artist. Performing Arts major (Thai International Music - Singing) for the year 2022 will be performed for the 12th time in 2023, the 37th year since the first Bird Bird Show concert, held at IMPACT. Arena Muang Thong Thani, initially scheduled to show 2 rounds on 18 and 19 November 2023, later added a charity round on 17 November because of these 3 rounds All tickets were sold out, so 2 more rounds were added on 25 and 26 November, for a total of 5 rounds.
response.title: Babb Bird Bird Show #12/2023 MULTIBIRD
